00070   resp->resop = NFS4_OP_SEQUENCE;

00073   /* OP_SEQUENCE is always the first operation of the request */

00113   if(arg_SEQUENCE4.sa_slotid >= psession->fore_channel_attrs.ca_maxrequests)
